<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4 0%, #0891b2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%), linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4 0%, #0891b2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .user-info {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            float: right;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        {{#if avatar}}
        <img src="{{avatar}}" alt="Profile Picture" class="avatar">
        {{/if}}
        
        <h2>Welcome to your learning adventure, {{firstName}}! ðŸŽ‰</h2>
        
        <p>This is such an exciting moment! Your {{companyName}} account is ready, and you're about to embark on a personalized learning journey designed just for you. We're not just another platform - we're your partners in growth, ready to help you unlock skills you didn't even know you had.</p>
        
        <div class="user-info">
            <h3>Your Account Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{recipientEmail}}</p>
            {{#if organizationName}}
            <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{organizationName}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if branchName}}
            <p><strong>Branch:</strong> {{branchName}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <h3>Your Learning Superpowers Await</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Tackle engaging tests and quizzes that adapt to your learning style</li>
            <li>Watch your progress unfold with detailed analytics and achievements</li>
            <li>Explore a rich library of learning materials curated for your success</li>
            <li>Customize your experience to match your goals and preferences</li>
            <li>Connect with fellow learners and expert mentors in your organization</li>
            <li>Celebrate milestones and track your continuous growth journey</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            <a href="{{profileUrl}}" class="button" style="background-color: #6c757d;">Edit Profile</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>Ready to transform your potential into expertise? <a href="{{loginUrl}}">Log in to your account</a> and discover a learning experience that's both powerful and enjoyable. Every click forward is a step toward the professional you're becoming!</p>
        
        <p>Questions? Excitement? Curiosity? We're here for all of it! Our friendly support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> loves helping learners succeed.</p>
        
        <p>Here's to your success and growth! ðŸš€<br>
        Your Learning Champions at {{companyName}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{recipientEmail}}</p>
        <p>{{companyName}} | <a href="{{companyUrl}}">{{companyUrl}}</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 